8IrefSu53T44xeEAMaCTEwMzExNDMxNyCnscarBjAAOCNAIHIJNjMzNzYwNTE1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1706617864.232259", "card_id": "Q_641941520", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美国得州副州长称将继续在美墨边境修建刀片刺网等屏障，如果执法部门干预，将会与其对抗，透露哪些信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "美国得州副州长称将继续在美墨边境修建刀片刺网等屏障 央视新闻消息，当地时间 1 月 29 日，美国得克萨斯州副州长帕特里克表示，该州将继续在美墨边境修建刀片刺网等屏障。 据悉，美国最高法院于上周下令允许边境巡逻队拆除该州边境设置的刀片刺网等屏障。对此，帕特里克称，该州正在尽一切努力继续搭建刀片刺网，如果执法部门对其进行拆除，该州将会与其「对抗」，同时更换新的屏障。美国得州副州长称将继续在美墨边境修建刀片刺网等屏障"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-41768b02bf7830ef6684deaac47f535d_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/641941520"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIrefSu53T44xeEAMaCTEwNDkzMTQ4MyCKmeGtBjAAOKwBQCFyCTY0MTk0MTUyMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "34_1706617864.234550", "card_id": "Q_641956217", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 91}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "23-24赛季NBA常规赛湖人119:135火箭，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[2 张图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7946326ee2d6f04500e1be1a8cd90b44_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/641956217"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IrefSu53T44xeEAMaCTEwNDkzNDcwNyCt2+GtBjAAOFpAInIJNjQxOTU2MjE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1706617864.235128", "card_id": "Q_617191681", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 190}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何判断一家公司是否是好公司呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最近面试了很多家公司，风格各不相同，有些公司规模小，但是模式制度照搬大厂；有些公司看着规模挺大，但是从面